<http://dx.doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.3927.1.1>
    bibo:endPage "117" ;
    bibo:issue "1" ;
    bibo:journal "Zootaxa" ;
    bibo:startPage "1" ;
    bibo:volume "3927" ;
    dc:creator "Koppka, Jens" ;
    dc:date "2015" ;
    dc:title "Revision of the Bivalvia from the Upper Jurassic Reuchenette Formation, Northwest Switzerland — Ostreoidea" ;
    fabio:hasPart <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288041>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288040>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288042>, <http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288038> ;
    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288041>
    dc:description "FIGURE 7. Circunula n. gen. cotyledon (Contejean, 1859). Ontogeny of ligament area (schematic). 1. LV, juvenile with a triangular, initially alivincular-areate ligament. 2. Recurving of the umbo (hypothetic). 3. Continuation of opisthogyrate twisting, ligament becomes prosodetic and opisthocline, posterior bourrelet overgrown by projection of the posterodorsal hinge margin; observations based on a group of juveniles (ALO 009 - 1 - I-IV, Figs. 6, 8). Scale x 5." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288041/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288040>
    dc:description "FIGURE 6. Circunula n. gen. cotyledon (Contejean, 1859). 1 – 3. Drawings of three juvenile specimens originally attached close together on a Trichites - shell (CGN-ALO 009 - 1, see Fig. 8; Pl. 3.2 – 3), Alombre aux Vaches near Courgenay, Lower Kimmeridgian: 1, LV, umbo prosogyrate, ALO 009 - 1 - II; 2, LV, opisthogyrate, ALO 009 - 1 - I; 3, LV, opisthogyrate, ALO 009 - 1 - III. Scale x 5." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288040/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288042>
    dc:description "FIGURE 8. Circunula n. gen. cotyledon (Contejean, 1859). Group of juvenile LVs attached interior, of a bivalved Trichites (CGN-ALO 009 - 1, largest oyster specimens labelled from I-IV, see also Fig. 6), close to its ventral margin; Alombre aux Vaches (Canton Jura), Lower Kimmeridgian, Banné Marls. Scale x 1.5." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288042/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.288038>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Litho- and biostratigraphy of the observed parts of the Reuchenette Formation in the Ajoie, with distribution of oysters and characteristic fossils. A. Synthetic section. B. Detailed section of the Banné Member in Vâ Tche Tchâ (VTT), Lower Kimmeridgian. C. Detailed section of the upper part of the Courtedoux Member and “ Lower Virgula Marl ”; based on Tchâfouè (TCH) and Sur Combe Ronde (SCR), Upper Kimmeridgian (note separate bed numeration for VTT and SCR / TCH)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/288038/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

